DAGGERHEART PRIMER — LICENSE & ATTRIBUTION NOTICE

This repository is an unofficial, non-commercial, fan-made project created
solely for learning and exploring the Daggerheart tabletop roleplaying game.

OWNERSHIP

Daggerheart(TM), the Daggerheart Core Rulebook, the Daggerheart System
